### Configuracoes Iniciais (Variaveis)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 0. Login para obter token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "contato@opticaflow.com.br",
  "senha": "11222333000181"
}

###

@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN
@empresaId = COLE_ID_EMPRESA
@filialId = COLE_ID_FILIAL
@clienteId = COLE_ID_CLIENTE
@atendimentoId = COLE_ID_ATENDIMENTO
@vendaId = COLE_ID_VENDA

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------
### VENDA
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Criar venda
POST {{baseUrl}}/venda
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "clienteId": "{{clienteId}}",
  "atendimentoId": "{{atendimentoId}}",
  "dataVenda": "2026-07-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "aberta",
  "observacoes": "Venda de teste"
}

### 2. Listar vendas por empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/venda/empresa/{{empresaId}}?page=1&limit=10&search=teste&filialId={{filialId}}&clienteId={{clienteId}}&atendimentoId={{atendimentoId}}&status=aberta
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Buscar venda por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/venda/{{vendaId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Atualizar venda
PUT {{baseUrl}}/venda/{{vendaId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "finalizada",
  "observacoes": "Venda conferida e finalizada"
}

### 5. Teste negativo: cliente de outra filial
POST {{baseUrl}}/venda
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "clienteId": "COLE_CLIENTE_DE_OUTRA_FILIAL"
}

### 6. Deletar venda (somente sem itens)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/venda/{{vendaId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
